CustomField.label: Add change monitor event count
CustomField.description: The number of times that the add change monitor event has happened. Each of these events correlates to somebody creating a change monitor job. This count can be higher than the number of currently configured jobs if they've then gone on to delete jobs
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The number of times that the add change monitor event has happened. Each of these events correlates to somebody creating a change monitor job. This count can be higher than the number of currently configured jobs if they've then gone on to delete jobs
